Business Layer Human Resources Information

General Information

Modified

Fri Sep 29 10:17:09 CDT 2017

Name

Human Resources Information

Description

Human Resource Information universe provides information about HR activities that happen daily at USAA.In addition to the daily activities , the universe provides Exit Interview information too.

case when instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,',',-1,1) > 0 and instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,'(inactive)',1,1) > 0 then substr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,1, instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' (inactive)',-1,1)) when instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,',',-1,1) > 0 then A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM when instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,'- NX',-1,1) > 0 then trim(substr(substr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,1,instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' - NX',-1,1)),1,instr(rtrim(substr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,1,instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' - NX',-1,1)),' '),' ',-1,1))) when instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,'(inactive)',-1,1) > 0 then trim(substr(substr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,1,instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' (inactive)',-1,1)),1,instr(rtrim(substr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,1,instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' (inactive)',-1,1)),' '),' ',-1,1))) else trim(substr(rtrim(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,'(inactive)'),1,instr(A_JOB_PROFILE.JOB_TITLE_NM,' ',-1,1))) END

SELECT DISTINCT A_BUSINESS_PROCESS_DAY.MONTH_NUM FROM PHRAEDB.ADMIN.M_CWF_DM_DAY A_BUSINESS_PROCESS_DAY INNER JOIN PHRAELB.ADMIN.M_CWF_LK_AS_OF_DATE A_LK_ASOFDATE_ACT ON (A_BUSINESS_PROCESS_DAY.DAY_DT<=A_LK_ASOFDATE_ACT.AS_OF_DT) WHERE ( A_BUSINESS_PROCESS_DAY.DAY_DT >= add_months(date_trunc('YEAR',( A_LK_ASOFDATE_ACT.UA_WF_LST_LOAD_DT ) ),-24) AND A_BUSINESS_PROCESS_DAY.DAY_DT <= ( A_LK_ASOFDATE_ACT.AS_OF_DT ) )
